%body
  %div{:"data-role" => 'page'}
    %div{:"data-role" => 'header', :"data-theme" => 'b'}
      %h1{:role => 'heading'}BARTtimes.com
      %a{:"data-rel" => 'dialog', :href => '#about', :"data-transition" => 'slidedown', :"data-icon" => 'info', :"data-iconpos" => "notext"}
    %div{:"data-role" => 'content'}
      %ul{ :"data-role" => 'listview', :"data-theme" => 'b', :"data-filter" => 'true'}
        - Bart::Station::LIST.each do |station_hash|
          %li
            %a{:href => "/station/" + station_hash[:id], :rel => 'external'} 
              = station_hash[:name]
  %div{:"data-role" => 'page', :id => 'about'}
    %div{:"data-role" => 'header', :"data-theme" => 'b' }
      %h1{:role => 'heading'} About
    %div{:"data-role" => 'content', :"data-theme" => 'b' }
      This mobile web app was built by Nicholas Fowler using the BART Data API, and the web magic provided by Ruby, the Sinatra framework, Haml, and jQuery Mobile.
